.TH LOOTSHEET-QUEST-COMPLETE 1 "Mar 2026" "LootSheet" "LootSheet Manual"
.SH NAME
lootsheet-quest-complete \\- Recognize a quest as earned
.SH SYNOPSIS
lootsheet quest complete [flags]
.SH DESCRIPTION
LootSheet CLI

Usage:
  lootsheet quest complete --id ID --date YYYY-MM-DD

Example:
  lootsheet quest complete --id quest-123 --date 2026-03-12
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--date=string
completed date in YYYY-MM-DD (required) (default: )
.TP
-h, --help
help for complete
.TP
--id=string
quest ID (required) (default: )
.SH SEE ALSO
lootsheet-quest(1)
